org.semanticweb.owl.align
Interface Parameters

All Known Implementing Classes:
BasicParameters
public interface Parameters

A set of parameters to be passed to an alignment or evaluation method. This interface is a minimal one: add, remove, get parameter value, get a list of available parameters as an enumeration. I does not provide any integrity checking (set and unset silently and erase the previous value is there were one). getParameter must return (null) if no corresponding parameter exist. JE: this may be deprecated at some point to use the standard Java java.lang.Properties class.
